{"type": "article", "id": 13435, "title": "多功能边桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-13T07:31:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155226pFTMKd7hq9u5aGrx.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“R35” 是一组形态各异的边桌，来自设计师 Verena Waidmann 和 Lukas Gstöttner。桌子使用金属制成，依据颜色和形态，分为 “paper”，“skate” 和 “loop” 三款。其中，“paper” 边上有一个凹槽，可以轻松把报纸搁在里面，“skate” 桌子中间有一个把手，方面人们移动桌子，“loop” 设计了一个小洞，可以放点儿私密或是容易丢的小物件。三款桌子看上去都十分简洁可爱。<a href=\"http://www.bonpart.at/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141214SjKmDn7LOcPoaEyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141215HqF3y0l64JCEutY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141215RMSzqHJr5PsFQgEN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141216MIus5fmQrNtjUOy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49755501\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141216mhkAcjbrlX1CvG97.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141217tpogxbuIOnivrQK6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n\n"}